# Socks5Proxies Free Proxy List

Daily snapshot of public proxy endpoints exported from Socks5Proxies.com.

> Latest snapshot: **{{TOTAL_ALL}}** proxies from **{{COUNTRY_COUNT}}** countries at **{{UPDATED_AT}}**.

## Why this repo exists

- GitHub is the distribution channel for daily snapshots.
- The live site is the better product surface for filtering, exports, and validation.
- If you came here from search, use the live site when you need fresher data than the GitHub snapshot.

